txt.en: Parth Duin is located east of Crithost.\n\nYou should destroy Easterling tents and destroy their barricades before the farm becomes a full fledged encampment.
Tolwin can be found in the hall of Crithost.\n\nYou should speak with Tolwin.
Destroy S没halar tents at Parth Duin ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
'Good work. I look up to your skills in turning the battle. It astounds me to think that you are able to take on many men by yourself.'

'Easterlings have taken the farm of Parth Duin, east of here. Are you willing to confront them and push their forces away from this farmland?\n\n'Destroy their structures to pay them back for what they've done to Cair Andros and my family.'
Easterlings have nearly destroyed Parth Duin, a farm east of Crithost. Tolwin is determined to show the Easterlings that they are not welcome in Talath Anor and asks you to give them this message.
